---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<footer class="mt-auto border-t border-sand-200/80 bg-sand-50">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-8 py-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-sand-500">
    <div>
      <p class="font-display text-base text-claude-brown mb-1">Claude Code Cheatsheet</p>
      <p>Fait avec Astro. Inspire par <a href="https://awesomeclaude.ai" class="text-claude-orange hover:underline underline-offset-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Awesome Claude</a>.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex gap-5">
      <a href="https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code" class="hover:text-claude-orange transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Docs officielles</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code" class="hover:text-claude-orange transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
